title: Age.of.Booty-OUTLAWS [Full Game]
description:
About Age of Booty

    * Genre: Action Strategy
    * Rating: E (Everyone)
    * Players: 1-8, up to 4 local
    * Platforms: Xbox Live Arcade, PlayStation Network, Windows
    * Price: $10 (all platforms)

Age of Booty is a downloadable real-time action strategy game from Certain Affinity and Capcom. Play alone, splitscreen, or with friends on a local network or online. Anyone can master the simple interface but only the most devious will become masters of the seas!

    * Sink enemies, seize towns, upgrade your ship, and use curses to foil your foes
    * Easy and intuitive console controls 
    * Up to 4 players split screen, up to 8 networked
    * Clever AI pirates that can play with you or against you
    * Tons of customizable options
    * Boatloads of single player challenges and multiplayer maps
    * Create your own maps and share them with friends
    * Just $10 on Xbox Live Arcade, PlayStation Network, and Windows  <a href="
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Age_of_Booty" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Age_of_Booty</a>
